snippet: BATE Borisov of Belarus stunned Bayern Munich in Minsk on Tuesday for its second win in two games of the Champions League.
abstract: BATE Borisov defeats Bayern Munich, 3-1, in Champions League soccer action; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: BATE Borisov of Belarus stunned Bayern Munich in Minsk on Tuesday for its second win in two games of the Champions League.
